## Run mlp.py to generate plots

linear.py:
    the reused Linear module

mlp.py:
    contains the MLP module and code to train the mlp model

mlp_tests.py:
    unit tests for the MLP module

boundary.png:
    the output graph of the decision boundary with threshold 0.5

surface.png:
    the output graph of the decision surface without thresholds

requirements.txt:
    contains all the site packages installed